snippet.title: White Supremacists in Patriot Front March Lack Rhythm: Week In Review | The Amber Ruffin
snippet.description:
The Amber Ruffin Show. New Episodes Streaming Every Friday on Peacock: https://pck.tv/3pOiao8

Reserve your spot in the live studio audience for The Amber Ruffin Show at https://1iota.com/show/1210/the-amber-ruffin-show

It has been a crazy week in America! On Saturday a group of white supremacists calling themselves the Patriot Front marched through Washington D.C., carrying American flags and chanting “Reclaim America.” We know this is a disturbing display of openly racist ideals, but can we talk about their complete lack of rhythm.

 #TheAmberRuffinShow #PeacockTV #WeekInReview
